data-triple-N3.o: "1984 was a leap year that started on a Sunday, in accordance with the Gregorian calendar. It is the 1984th year of the Common Era or A.D. ; the 984th year of the 2nd millennium; the 84th year of the 20th century; and the 5th year of the 1980s decade."@en
